=== dependencies ===
libgsl
libm
libcfitsio
libcblas
libcurses
libqhull
python2.7
cmake


==== Compilation ===

osx only :
export CC=/opt/local/bin/gcc-mp-5.8

cd build
cmake ../
make


=== Input ( default provided ) ===
build/doc/example/input.ini
doc/example/model.py
data/jena_thin_e6.tab is used in current input.ini

=== Execution ===
./lime build/doc/example/input.ini

